# 🧮 Calculator with Theme Toggle

A modern, responsive calculator built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, featuring a clean neumorphic UI and a dark/light theme toggle.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔢 Basic arithmetic operations (+, −, ×, ÷)
- 🖥️ Interactive display screen
- 🖱️ Clickable buttons
- ⌨️ Full keyboard support
- 🌗 Dark / Light theme toggle
- 💾 Theme preference saved using `localStorage`
- 🎨 Neumorphism-inspired modern UI

---

## ⌨️ Keyboard Shortcuts

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `0-9` | Enter numbers |
| `+ - * /` | Operators |
| `Enter` | Calculate result |
| `Backspace` | Delete last digit |
| `C` | Clear display |
| `.` | Decimal input |


---

## 🌗 Theme Toggle

- Click the 🌙 button to switch between **Light** and **Dark** mode
- Your selected theme is automatically saved and restored on reload

---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Custom Properties / Variables)
- Vanilla JavaScript

